OL,3,CNHS Trust seeing A&E demand 'no other
OL,4,Chospital has'
OL,6,FAn NHS trust said it is seeing
OL,7,Fincreases in ambulances coming into
OL,8,Fits hospitals and "unprecedented
OL,9,Fdemand" at Accident and Emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments.
OL,12,FWirral University Teaching Hospitals
OL,13,FNHS Foundation Trust told Wirral
OL,14,Fcouncillors it is trying to understand
OL,15,Fwhat is causing a 20% increase in
OL,16,Fpatients turning up at A&E.
