OL,3,CNHS Trust seeing A&E demand 'no other
OL,4,Chospital has'
OL,6,FThe NHS trust, which manages both
OL,7,FArrowe Park and Clatterbridge
OL,8,FHospitals on the Wirral, recently
OL,9,Fdeclared an internal critical
OL,10,Fincident, otherwise referred to a
OL,11,Fbusiness continuity incident.
OL,13,FThis was due to "the ongoing
OL,14,Funprecedented demand" at Arrowe Park's
OL,15,Femergency department which was "more
OL,16,Fthan we have experienced in any winter
OL,17,Fperiod".
OL,19,FThe Trust employs over 6,000 staff and
OL,20,Fcurrently has a capacity of around 800
OL,21,Fbeds, all of which are currently full.
