OL,3,CNHS Trust seeing A&E demand 'no other
OL,4,Chospital has'
OL,6,FThe trust appeared before Wirral
OL,7,Fcouncillors at an adult health and
OL,8,Fsocial care meeting, where councillors
OL,9,Fquestioned whether the trust was
OL,10,Fprepared for winter "with all the
OL,11,Fpressures that the hospitals are
OL,12,Funder."
OL,14,FDr Nikki Stevenson, executive medical
OL,15,Fdirector at the trust, said the trust
OL,16,Fwas drawing up plans to create
OL,17,Fcapacity, adding: "The demands on the
OL,18,FNHS this year have been winter all
OL,19,Fyear round but this year we are all
OL,20,Fexperiencing it.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@GO]yD@SOU
