OL,3,CNHS Trust seeing A&E demand 'no other
OL,4,Chospital has'
OL,6,F"We have an increase in respiratory
OL,7,Fviruses, it's getting colder. We know
OL,8,Fto anticipate that."
OL,10,FShe said the trust was taking people
OL,11,Finto the hospital so that ambulance
OL,12,Fcrews could go back out and respond to
OL,13,Fcalls, adding: "It's really scary if
OL,14,Fyou're at home and you phone for an
OL,15,Fambulance and it doesn't come."
OL,17,FShe admitted this did lead to corridor
OL,18,Fcare but argued leaving patients
OL,19,Fwaiting in ambulances was unacceptable.
