OL,6,FShe said the trust had been visited by
OL,7,FNHS England to look at the emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment because the Wirral had seen
OL,9,Fa 20% increase in ambulances
OL,10,Ftransporting people to hospital,
OL,11,Fadding; "No other hospital has seen
OL,12,Fthat so there's something that's going
OL,13,Fon there so we're just trying to
OL,14,Funderstand what it is."
